{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":0,"text":"This is my first trip,"},{"time":2000,"text":"my first foreign trip as a first lady."},{"time":4000,"text":"Can you believe that?"},{"time":6000,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":16000,"text":"And while this is not my first visit to the U.K.,"},{"time":19000,"text":"I have to say that I am glad that this is my first official visit."},{"time":24000,"text":"The special relationship between the United States and the U.K."},{"time":28000,"text":"is based not only on the relationship between governments,"},{"time":33000,"text":"but the common language and the values that we share,"},{"time":36000,"text":"and I'm reminded of that by watching you all today."},{"time":40000,"text":"During my visit I've been especially honored"},{"time":44000,"text":"to meet some of Britain's most extraordinary women --"},{"time":47000,"text":"women who are paving the way for all of you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":50000,"text":"And I'm honored to meet you,"},{"time":53000,"text":"the future leaders of Great Britain and this world."},{"time":59000,"text":"And although the circumstances of our lives may seem very distant,"},{"time":64000,"text":"with me standing here as the First Lady of the United States of America,"},{"time":68000,"text":"and you, just getting through school,"},{"time":72000,"text":"I want you to know that we have very much in common."},{"time":76000,"text":"For nothing in my life's path"},{"time":80000,"text":"would have predicted that I'd be standing here"},{"time":82000,"text":"as the first African-American First Lady"},{"time":85000,"text":"of the United States of America."},{"time":87000,"text":"There is nothing in my story that would land me here."},{"time":92000,"text":"I wasn't raised with wealth or resources"},{"time":95000,"text":"or any social standing to speak of."},{"time":99000,"text":"I was raised on the South Side of Chicago."},{"time":103000,"text":"That's the real part of Chicago."},{"time":106000,"text":"And I was the product of a working-class community."},{"time":109000,"text":"My father was a city worker all of his life,"},{"time":113000,"text":"and my mother was a stay-at-home mom."},{"time":115000,"text":"And she stayed at home to take care of me and my older brother."},{"time":120000,"text":"Neither of them attended university."},{"time":123000,"text":"My dad was diagnosed with multiple sclerosis"},{"time":126000,"text":"in the prime of his life."},{"time":128000,"text":"But even as it got harder for him to walk"},{"time":131000,"text":"and get dressed in the morning --"},{"time":133000,"text":"I saw him struggle more and more --"},{"time":135000,"text":"my father never complained about his struggle."},{"time":139000,"text":"He was grateful for what he had."},{"time":141000,"text":"He just woke up a little earlier and worked a little harder."},{"time":146000,"text":"And my brother and I were raised with all that you really need:"},{"time":149000,"text":"love, strong values"},{"time":152000,"text":"and a belief that with a good education"},{"time":155000,"text":"and a whole lot of hard work,"},{"time":157000,"text":"that there was nothing that we could not do."}]},{"cues":[{"time":160000,"text":"I am an example of what's possible"},{"time":164000,"text":"when girls from the very beginning of their lives"},{"time":168000,"text":"are loved and nurtured by the people around them."},{"time":173000,"text":"I was surrounded by extraordinary women in my life:"},{"time":177000,"text":"grandmothers, teachers, aunts, cousins, neighbors,"},{"time":182000,"text":"who taught me about quiet strength and dignity."},{"time":186000,"text":"And my mother, the most important role model in my life,"},{"time":191000,"text":"who lives with us at the White House"},{"time":193000,"text":"and helps to care for our two little daughters,"},{"time":196000,"text":"Malia and Sasha."},{"time":198000,"text":"She's an active presence in their lives, as well as mine,"},{"time":202000,"text":"and is instilling in them"},{"time":204000,"text":"the same values that she taught me and my brother:"},{"time":207000,"text":"things like compassion, and integrity,"},{"time":210000,"text":"and confidence, and perseverance --"},{"time":214000,"text":"all of that wrapped up in an unconditional love"},{"time":217000,"text":"that only a grandmother can give."}]},{"cues":[{"time":220000,"text":"I was also fortunate enough to be cherished and encouraged"},{"time":224000,"text":"by some strong male role models as well,"},{"time":229000,"text":"including my father, my brother, uncles and grandfathers."},{"time":232000,"text":"The men in my life taught me some important things, as well."},{"time":237000,"text":"They taught me about what a respectful relationship"},{"time":240000,"text":"should look like between men and women."},{"time":244000,"text":"They taught me about what a strong marriage feels like:"},{"time":248000,"text":"that it's built on faith and commitment"},{"time":251000,"text":"and an admiration for each other's unique gifts."},{"time":255000,"text":"They taught me about what it means"},{"time":257000,"text":"to be a father"},{"time":259000,"text":"and to raise a family."},{"time":261000,"text":"And not only to invest in your own home"},{"time":263000,"text":"but to reach out and help raise kids"},{"time":268000,"text":"in the broader community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":270000,"text":"And these were the same qualities"},{"time":272000,"text":"that I looked for in my own husband,"},{"time":275000,"text":"Barack Obama."},{"time":278000,"text":"And when we first met,"},{"time":281000,"text":"one of the things that I remember is that he took me out on a date."},{"time":285000,"text":"And his date was to go with him to a community meeting."},{"time":288000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":290000,"text":"I know, how romantic."},{"time":292000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":295000,"text":"But when we met, Barack was a community organizer."},{"time":297000,"text":"He worked, helping people to find jobs"},{"time":301000,"text":"and to try to bring resources into struggling neighborhoods."},{"time":305000,"text":"As he talked to the residents in that community center,"},{"time":307000,"text":"he talked about two concepts."},{"time":309000,"text":"He talked about \"the world as it is\" and \"the world as it should be.\""},{"time":315000,"text":"And I talked about this throughout the entire campaign."},{"time":319000,"text":"What he said, that all too often,"},{"time":321000,"text":"is that we accept the distance between those two ideas."},{"time":326000,"text":"And sometimes we settle for the world as it is,"},{"time":330000,"text":"even when it doesn't reflect our values and aspirations."},{"time":334000,"text":"But Barack reminded us on that day,"},{"time":337000,"text":"all of us in that room, that we all know"},{"time":340000,"text":"what our world should look like."},{"time":344000,"text":"We know what fairness and justice and opportunity look like."},{"time":347000,"text":"We all know."},{"time":349000,"text":"And he urged the people in that meeting,"},{"time":351000,"text":"in that community,"},{"time":353000,"text":"to devote themselves to closing the gap"},{"time":356000,"text":"between those two ideas,"},{"time":358000,"text":"to work together to try to make the world as it is"},{"time":362000,"text":"and the world as it should be, one and the same."}]},{"cues":[{"time":366000,"text":"And I think about that today because I am"},{"time":369000,"text":"reminded and convinced that all of you in this school"},{"time":373000,"text":"are very important parts of closing that gap."},{"time":378000,"text":"You are the women who will build the world as it should be."},{"time":383000,"text":"You're going to write the next chapter in history."},{"time":385000,"text":"Not just for yourselves, but for your generation"},{"time":389000,"text":"and generations to come."},{"time":392000,"text":"And that's why getting a good education"},{"time":394000,"text":"is so important."},{"time":396000,"text":"That's why all of this that you're going through --"},{"time":399000,"text":"the ups and the downs, the teachers that you love and the teachers that you don't --"},{"time":403000,"text":"why it's so important."},{"time":406000,"text":"Because communities and countries and ultimately the world"},{"time":409000,"text":"are only as strong as the health of their women."},{"time":414000,"text":"And that's important to keep in mind."}]},{"cues":[{"time":416000,"text":"Part of that health includes an outstanding education."},{"time":422000,"text":"The difference between a struggling family and a healthy one"},{"time":427000,"text":"is often the presence of an empowered woman"},{"time":430000,"text":"or women at the center of that family."},{"time":433000,"text":"The difference between a broken community and a thriving one"},{"time":436000,"text":"is often the healthy respect between men and women"},{"time":440000,"text":"who appreciate the contributions each other makes to society."},{"time":445000,"text":"The difference between a languishing nation"},{"time":448000,"text":"and one that will flourish"},{"time":450000,"text":"is the recognition that we need equal access to education"},{"time":454000,"text":"for both boys and girls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":456000,"text":"And this school, named after the U.K.'s first female doctor,"},{"time":461000,"text":"and the surrounding buildings named for Mexican artist Frida Kahlo,"},{"time":467000,"text":"Mary Seacole,"},{"time":469000,"text":"the Jamaican nurse known as the \"black Florence Nightingale,\""},{"time":473000,"text":"and the English author, Emily Bronte,"},{"time":476000,"text":"honor women who fought sexism, racism and ignorance,"},{"time":480000,"text":"to pursue their passions to feed their own souls."},{"time":485000,"text":"They allowed for no obstacles."},{"time":488000,"text":"As the sign said back there, \"without limitations.\""},{"time":492000,"text":"They knew no other way to live"},{"time":494000,"text":"than to follow their dreams."},{"time":497000,"text":"And having done so, these women"},{"time":502000,"text":"moved many obstacles."},{"time":504000,"text":"And they opened many new doors"},{"time":506000,"text":"for millions of female doctors and nurses"},{"time":509000,"text":"and artists and authors,"},{"time":512000,"text":"all of whom have followed them."},{"time":514000,"text":"And by getting a good education,"},{"time":517000,"text":"you too can control your own destiny."}]},{"cues":[{"time":521000,"text":"Please remember that."},{"time":524000,"text":"If you want to know the reason why I'm standing here,"},{"time":528000,"text":"it's because of education."},{"time":531000,"text":"I never cut class. Sorry, I don't know if anybody is cutting class."},{"time":535000,"text":"I never did it."},{"time":537000,"text":"I loved getting As."},{"time":539000,"text":"I liked being smart."},{"time":541000,"text":"I liked being on time. I liked getting my work done."},{"time":545000,"text":"I thought being smart was cooler than anything in the world."},{"time":550000,"text":"And you too, with these same values,"},{"time":552000,"text":"can control your own destiny."},{"time":554000,"text":"You too can pave the way."},{"time":557000,"text":"You too can realize your dreams,"},{"time":559000,"text":"and then your job is to reach back"},{"time":563000,"text":"and to help someone just like you do the same thing."},{"time":567000,"text":"History proves that it doesn't matter"},{"time":570000,"text":"whether you come from a council estate"},{"time":572000,"text":"or a country estate."}]},{"cues":[{"time":574000,"text":"Your success will be determined"},{"time":576000,"text":"by your own fortitude,"},{"time":579000,"text":"your own confidence, your own individual hard work."},{"time":583000,"text":"That is true. That is the reality of the world that we live in."},{"time":587000,"text":"You now have control over your own destiny."},{"time":590000,"text":"And it won't be easy -- that's for sure."},{"time":595000,"text":"But you have everything you need."},{"time":597000,"text":"Everything you need to succeed,"},{"time":600000,"text":"you already have, right here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":603000,"text":"My husband works in this big office."},{"time":607000,"text":"They call it the Oval Office."},{"time":610000,"text":"In the White House, there's the desk that he sits at --"},{"time":612000,"text":"it's called the Resolute desk."},{"time":615000,"text":"It was built by the timber of Her Majesty's Ship Resolute"},{"time":619000,"text":"and given by Queen Victoria."},{"time":622000,"text":"It's an enduring symbol of the friendship between our two nations."},{"time":627000,"text":"And its name, Resolute,"},{"time":629000,"text":"is a reminder of the strength of character that's required"},{"time":633000,"text":"not only to lead a country,"},{"time":635000,"text":"but to live a life of purpose, as well."},{"time":640000,"text":"And I hope in pursuing your dreams, you all remain resolute,"},{"time":644000,"text":"that you go forward without limits,"},{"time":647000,"text":"and that you use your talents -- because there are many; we've seen them;"},{"time":652000,"text":"it's there --"},{"time":654000,"text":"that you use them to create the world as it should be."},{"time":658000,"text":"Because we are counting on you."},{"time":661000,"text":"We are counting on every single one of you"},{"time":663000,"text":"to be the very best that you can be."},{"time":666000,"text":"Because the world is big."},{"time":668000,"text":"And it's full of challenges."},{"time":670000,"text":"And we need strong, smart, confident young women"},{"time":674000,"text":"to stand up and take the reins."}]},{"cues":[{"time":676000,"text":"We know you can do it. We love you. Thank you so much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":680000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}